title: Lakeside is waiting for you! Come live on the lake and call today!
posting_body: ['Start you story at Lakeside in Everett, WA!', 'A beautiful community steps away from local parks, dining, shopping and Everett’s largest employer Boeing!', 'Right on Beverly Lake!', 'All Lakeside apartment homes come equipped with washers and dryers, balconies, and fireplaces.', 'Fall in love with our fully-equipped gourmet kitchens!', 'We are ready to do all we can to help you with your home search.', 'Please call or email us today to see how you can schedule a virtual or in-person tour!', "This won't last long, call, text or today!!", 'Amenities', '•\tAssigned parking', '•\tIn-unit laundry', 'Details', '•\tBeds/Baths: 2BD/1BA', '•\tSquare Feet: 863', 'Rental Terms', '•\tRent: $1,985.00', '•\tAvailable: Call for availability', '•\tApplication Fee: $50.00', '•\tSecurity Deposit: $500.00', '•\tFlex-pay rent payments, making half-payments at the beginning and in the middle of the month!', 'Pet Policy', '•\tCats allowed', '•\tDogs allowed', '*Note images may not be of exact available apartment and may be of similar floorplan.', 'Finishes may differ.', 'Contact office staff to schedule a tour!']
